attributes.title: Mortal Kombat Rap - "Finish Him!"
attributes.caption: X-ray vision was a pretty awesome feature in this game...so naturally we made a song that glorified that.
attributes.description: X-ray vision was a pretty awesome feature in this game...so naturally we made a song that glorified that.

attributes.title: Gears of War 3 Rap - "This is Gears of War"
attributes.caption: This Gears Rap highlights the 3rd game and its story.
attributes.description: This Gears Rap highlights the 3rd game and its story.
attributes.display_title: Gears of War 3 Rap - "This is Gears of War"

attributes.title: Dead Island Song - "Welcome To Dead Island"
attributes.caption: Dead Island...it had a fun aesthetic and setting, but gave us headaches when we played. This song reflects that pretty well.
attributes.description: Dead Island...it had a fun aesthetic and setting, but gave us headaches when we played. This song reflects that pretty well.
attributes.display_title: Dead Island Song - "Welcome To Dead Island"

attributes.title: Battlefield 3 Rap - "Get Outta My Battlefield"
attributes.caption: This song was actually part of a shift away from "nerdcore" that we tried doing. The aim was to be more goofy such as "The Greatest Ever" was. We soon realized nerdcore was what the people wanted. Anyways, enjoy this BF3 Rap!
attributes.description: This song was actually part of a shift away from "nerdcore" that we tried doing. The aim was to be more goofy such as "The Greatest Ever" was. We soon realized nerdcore was what the people wanted. Anyways, enjoy this BF3 Rap!

attributes.title: Battlefield 3 Song - "I'll Get Your Dog Tags"
attributes.caption: Dogtags = Bragging rights in Battlefield. We chose to make a song with that in mind.
attributes.description: Dogtags = Bragging rights in Battlefield. We chose to make a song with that in mind.
attributes.display_title: Battlefield 3 Song - "I'll Get Your Dog Tags"

attributes.title: Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 3 Rap - I'm a G in CODMOD 3"
attributes.caption: Another more goofy rap (instead of nerdcore) and this song serves as a pretty good satirical piece for the obnoxious fanbase that CoD grew into having.
attributes.description: Another more goofy rap (instead of nerdcore) and this song serves as a pretty good satirical piece for the obnoxious fanbase that CoD grew into having.
attributes.display_title: Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 3 Rap - I'm a G in CODMOD 3"

attributes.title: Rage Rap - "Road Rage"
attributes.caption: This is potentially our all time least viewed rap. It makes sense when you see what song the game is about: Rage. This game was a perfect example of how long development cycles are detrimental to, well, everything.
attributes.description: This is potentially our all time least viewed rap. It makes sense when you see what song the game is about: Rage. This game was a perfect example of how long development cycles are detrimental to, well, everything.

attributes.title: Assassin's Creed 2: Revelations Rap - "The Hooded Assassin"
attributes.caption: Ezio was a badass and probably deserved twenty more songs. But alas, you get just this one.
attributes.description: Ezio was a badass and probably deserved twenty more songs. But alas, you get just this one.
attributes.display_title: Assassin's Creed 2: Revelations Rap - "The Hooded Assassin"

attributes.title: Batman Arkham City Rap - "The Bat Rap"
attributes.caption: Batman is a badass and The Bat Rap song has a jazzy take on his baddassery.
attributes.description: Batman is a badass and The Bat Rap song has a jazzy take on his baddassery.
attributes.display_title: Batman Arkham City Rap - "The Bat Rap"

attributes.title: Saints Row The Third Rap
attributes.caption: Saints Row The Third is a hot mess in all the right ways and this song matches the game's energy with a ritzy twist.
attributes.description: Saints Row The Third is a hot mess in all the right ways and this song matches the game's energy with a ritzy twist.

attributes.title: Call of Duty Black Ops Rap
attributes.caption: Call of Duty really started getting stale at this point, but that doesn't stop this Black Ops song from being fire.
attributes.description: Call of Duty really started getting stale at this point, but that doesn't stop this Black Ops song from being fire.
attributes.display_title: Call of Duty Black Ops Rap
